{"tid":2044189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"３月民調　５人１港獨　而泛黃中　支持者多　中立其次　反對者少","createTime":"2020-05-31T03:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T08:11:41.000Z","uid":261647,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f074a1e254c31d0fd23d7a1590f9c601256ec418","tid":2044189,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28716/港獨-2047-28716/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F28716%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-2047-28716%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=797206a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28716/港獨-2047-28716/</a><br />\n<br />\n最近，一份路透社委託香港民意研究所進行的民意調查發現，對比2019年12月的數字，反對香港獨立的比率由68％急劇下降至56％，對港獨持中立立場的香港人則由上年12月的9％升至18％。雖然支持港獨的比率只由上年12月的17％微升至現在的20％，但將整個民意調查結果綜合起來理解，我們大致可以歸納出「香港人逐漸不抗拒香港獨立」的趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2020/01/港獨-20200113074112_5718_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F01%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-20200113074112_5718_large.jpg&h=c1623a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每5個香港人就有1個支持香港獨立。如果「黃藍64比」以及「藍絲必定反對香港獨立」這兩個前設成立的話，我們可以推測這20％支持港獨的人應是來自支持抗爭的陣營。換個角度來想，如果上述兩個前設成立的話，56％的香港人反對港獨，若40％是來自藍營，那就只有16％是來自支持抗爭的陣營。若然那18％對港獨持中立立場的香港人都是來自支持抗爭的陣營，那麼我們就可以得出以下結論：「在支持抗爭陣營中，支持香港獨立的人最多，其次是持中立立場，反對的人最少。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200328/O5CG777AXWI3NSVNCJQK4PDNAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200328%2FO5CG777AXWI3NSVNCJQK4PDNAE%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=fac83162\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200328%2FO5CG777AXWI3NSVNCJQK4PDNAE%2F&h=44d12172\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200328/O5CG777AXWI3NSVNCJQK4PDNAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n2020.03.28<br />\n<br />\n今次是香港民意研究所於本月17至20日進行的新一輪調查，隨機電話訪問。<br />\n<br />\n對於港獨的態度，支持港獨的受訪者由去年12月調查的17%升至今次的20%。"},{"pid":"3dc30e197e11c338ad089fde01fbbd091187c0c9","tid":2044189,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"好彩個呢啲升幅唔係穩定升幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以一下爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快有Glory hunter架啦"},{"pid":"a136a092ec322398c2f7454fd01ec307696e482a","tid":2044189,"uid":1159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得中立或者不反對嗰啲覺得脫離到中國統治就得，獨唔獨立冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002f7b9fdf3b85d036b2ac324a25cfe484d24b92","tid":2044189,"uid":41355,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:33:59.000Z","msg":"本身泛民都畀中共逼到變港獨"},{"pid":"982b96d557f81ffab2c497276acc14da7cb9709f","tid":2044189,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，港獨從來都係共產黨助攻"},{"pid":"f526d8a3d392809e9d5e01d412defd7e6fe2271f","tid":2044189,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a136a092ec322398c2f7454fd01ec307696e482a","tid":2044189,"uid":1159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得中立或者不反對嗰啲覺得脫離到中國統治就得，獨唔獨立冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"本身一國兩制咪係咁<br />\n係中共on9"},{"pid":"58e5affe074fd96aad58b088aabc8bf84db76c3e","tid":2044189,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"982b96d557f81ffab2c497276acc14da7cb9709f","tid":2044189,"uid"