/>"},{"pid":"7104e9b8af2549f67dc2a297d92833ef8bdfe540","tid":2044189,"uid":135628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:05:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6a2981ebb387ac1b2d7f48960e581eba1c9c7c8","tid":2044189,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"呢個真，越黎越多人嗌。"},{"pid":"8c1b9b77ce9fcfa7a6dd7a72b41d112264901921","tid":2044189,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"982b96d557f81ffab2c497276acc14da7cb9709f","tid":2044189,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，港獨從來都係共產黨助攻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"國安法都立埋<br />\n仲助咩攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdf4a21b1b800f840c7471342a0651c992a9875","tid":2044189,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"但係咁樣比好危險<br />\n<br />\n你都識講&mdash;黃藍64比<br />\n黃本身都唔係多人過藍好多<br />\n如果係黃入邊再分裂<br />\n就會變成民調所講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">20(港獨)</span>:<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">18(中立)</span>:<span style=\"color: blue;\">56(反港獨)</span></span></strong><br />\n咁樣好容易比為中共入<br />\n我哋已經打唔贏黑警，如果冇埋民意支持，咁場運動就真係收得皮<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以即使支持港獨嘅你地唔想都好，但為咗抗爭着想，<span style=\"color: red;\">為咗最終目標着想，都要暫時收一收斂你哋嘅主張</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">比個班黃但係中立or反港獨嘅知道我哋短期目標係一致，應該繼續一齊團結對抗中共</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n屌佢地係冇用，民意調查已經幫你查清楚唔同立場嘅比例，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em>事實擺咗係度，唔會你玩晦氣屌幾句就改變</em></span></strong></span>，除咗你條氣順同埋令佢哋睇到更加不爽之外，對港獨最終目標冇任何幫助<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">倒不如諗吓點樣接受現實，調整策略、發揮優勢仲好</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">場運動應該係要強調共識，收窄分歧</span></strong></span><br />\n只有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">6(黃)</span>:<span style=\"color: blue;\">4(藍)</span></strong></span><br />\n先有機會贏到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單攞個比喻<br />\n港獨同埋中立係中共同國民黨，反港獨係日軍<br />\n咁中共同國民黨點都要夾手夾腳打贏日本先，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為兩者無論最終目標幾唔同</strong></span>，都要先趕走日軍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講要跳出同溫層<br />\n連登絕對係一個同溫層，令你覺得全香港都係深黃、支持獨立<br />\n但事實上係上次區議會選舉入邊黃藍得票比例都係得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">160萬</span>:<span style=\"color: blue;\">120萬</strong></span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><strong>差距唔係想像中咁大</strong></em></span><br />\n全香港有700幾萬人，最大陣營根本就係中立港豬，有時間內鬥不如感化佢地，令佢哋支持我哋仲好"},{"pid":"297f2d14ebfe5514e4f698e28fffad312794c8c2","tid":2044189,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831 打死人<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n唯一生路</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0e1d3fece752bb2a72ab794a38944e822a22018f","tid":2044189,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5031b15575fd352788da12b98c1a87a1b1926c7c","tid":2044189,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f526d8a3d392809e9d5e01d412defd7e6fe2271f","tid":2044189,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a136a092ec322398c2f7454fd01ec307696e482a","tid":2044189,"uid":1159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得中立或者不反對嗰啲覺得脫離到中國統治就得，獨唔獨立冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"本身一國兩制咪係咁<br />\n係中共on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"97主流民意都係維持現狀<br />\n係比班大中華膠民主建設中國同奶共商人騎劫成個香港上左賊船"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢班人死十次唔夠"},{"pid":"5608ccf39249e2e6144dff616db9c73b4971d6a5","tid":2044189,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a136a092ec322398c2f7454fd01ec307696e482a","tid":2044189,"uid":1159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得中立或者不反對嗰啲覺得脫離到中國統治就得，獨唔獨立冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"緊係唔係 係覺得同知道港獨冇可能成事啫 越搞越衰"},{"pid":"703faab4103e6b95b012fc85b0a9c2f453f8b5f1","tid":2044189,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"呢個係現實 現階段只有20%<br />\n<br />\n有班on9 想用自己係80%個玩法"},{"pid":"a7f75bea63b05916c7ef411b79b62a49159c90dc","tid":2044189,"uid":34804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"香港獨立既問題係無plan，無願景。<br />\n美屬/獨立/自治/改革/歸英<br />\n都係得個講字，好難令人信服。"}]}